## 📊 Optimization Rule Framework
The system operates on a precise classification matrix to maximize efficiency:

| Battery State-of-Health (SoH) | State-of-Charge (SoC) | Optimized Action Matrix |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **> 90% (Premium)** | $\ge$ 85% | Allocate to high-demand vehicles (**Cars**) |
| **60% - 85% (Standard)** | $\ge$ 85% | Allocate to light-demand vehicles (**Bikes/Autos**) |
| **50% - 60% (Low)** | Any % | Restrict to emergency backup only |
| **< 50% (Degraded)** | Any % | Flag for **Decommissioning & Recycling** |

